# Files copied into each new worktree created by `claude --worktree`.
# These are gitignored, so a fresh worktree would otherwise start without the
# maintainer's local permissions, wired hooks, and environment. Listing them
# here makes parallel-agent sessions inherit the same local setup.
#
# Tracked config (.claude/settings.json, .mcp.json) already appears in every
# worktree via the normal checkout — it does NOT need to be listed here.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/hooks/
.env*
